</td><td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:avoid" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_fa3d31c9-4b08-0e37-ce05-a5eb050f71bb" id="_fa3d31c9-4b08-0e37-ce05-a5eb050f71bb"></a><i><span class="blue">ECDIS Symbol</span></i></p>
